               <br/>
               Interdisciplinary Teams
              </h3>
             </div>
             <div class="col30 last floatLeft">
              <h3>
               <img alt="dollar_sign" src="/files/upload/sqr_arrow_icon.png" style="width: 53px; height: 53px; border-width: 0px; margin: 10px;"/>
