   <div class="howcanwe">
    <div class="wrapper">
     <div class="news">
      <h2 class="element-invisible">
       How can we help?
      </h2>
      <div class="region region-howcanwe">
       <div class="block block-block" id="block-block-13">
        <div class="content">
         <h2 align="center">
          How can we help?
         </h2>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="block block-block" id="block-block-15">
        <div class="content">
         <p class="rtecenter">
          The Office of Proposal Development is a service unit, working with Illinois faculty and other researchers to prepare proposals to secure external funding. The Office of Proposal Development provides comprehensive project management and proposal development services to support the preparation and submission of large-scale, interdisciplinary proposals. We help Illinois faculty members and other researchers to identify funding opportunities, coordinate interdisciplinary teams, develop compelling proposals, connect with relevant university resources, and secure external funding. The OPD is also a resource for the campus grants development community, serving as an information clearinghouse and repository for best practices in the field.
         </p>
         <p class="rtecenter">
          <a href="mailto:mme@illinois.edu?subject=OPD%20Information%20Request">
           Contact us
          </a>
          to discuss your specific needs.
         </p>
         <div class="col31 first floatleft">
          <h3>
           <a href="/grant-writing-advice" title="Grant-Writing Advice">
            Grant-Writing Advice
           </a>
          </h3>
         </div>
         <div class="col31 floatleft">
          <h3>
           <a href="/funding-agency-guidelines-advice" title="Funding Agency Guidance">
            Funding Agency Guidance
           </a>
          </h3>
         </div>
         <div class="col31 last floatleft">
          <h3>
           <a href="https://dev.proposal.illinois.edu/outreach-and-broader-impacts">
            Outreach and Broader Impacts
           </a>
          </h3>
         </div>
         <p>
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
